bulizer medication (such as albuterol)?</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://loinc.org/82673-5/\">82673-5</a></td><td>Como avaliaria o seu controlo da asma nas últimas 4 semanas?</td><td>How would you rate your asthma control during the past 4 weeks?</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://loinc.org/82668-5/\">82668-5</a></td><td>Pontuação total</td><td>Total score [ACT]</td><td>Score total</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
